main event: A student reported seeing an unidentified flying object over Highland Heights, Kentucky, which appeared as a white light in the sky and exhibited a jiggling motion.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on 31 March 1966 at approximately 1035 hours,The object was observed for around 10 minutes,The student used binoculars to enhance the view of the object,The object was seen to be at an extremely high altitude,The report indicated no complaints or issues related to the sighting from local authorities.
sighted object: a white light in the sky
witness description: a student from Villa Madonna, Covington, Kentucky
